Given an array, find the largest element .
Example:
arr = [3, 7, 2, 9, 5]
Output: 9

let arr = [3, 7, 2, 9, 5];
let largest = arr[0];   // assume first element is largest
for (let i = 1; i < arr.length; i++) {
    if (arr[i] > largest) {
        largest = arr[i];
    }
}
console.log("Largest element is:", largest);

Time Complexity: O(n) ‚Üí one loop used
Space Complexity: O(1) ‚Üí no extra space therefore O(1)
